  "faqBookingSection": "Booking",
  "faqHowToBook": "How do I book a ride?",
  "faqHowToBookAnswer": "Open the app, tap 'Where to?', enter your destination, choose a booking mode (Instant or Marketplace), select a payment method, and tap 'Find my driver'. A nearby driver will be matched to your ride.",
  "faqInstantVsMarketplace": "What is the difference between Instant and Marketplace?",
  "faqInstantVsMarketplaceAnswer": "Instant sends your ride request to nearby drivers immediately. Marketplace lets you set your own price and drivers can bid on your ride, potentially saving you money.",
  "faqScheduleRide": "Can I schedule a ride for later?",
  "faqScheduleRideAnswer": "Yes! Tap the 'Later' button on the home screen to choose a date and time for your ride. Your request will be sent to drivers at the scheduled time.",
  "faqHowMarketplace": "How does the Marketplace work?",
  "faqHowMarketplaceAnswer": "You set your desired price for the ride. Drivers see your offer and can bid on it. You choose which driver to accept based on their price, rating, and ETA.",
  "faqDriversSection": "Drivers and favourites",
  "faqAddFavourite": "How do I add a driver as a favourite?",
  "faqAddFavouriteAnswer": "After completing a ride, you can tap the heart icon on the rating screen to add that driver to your favourites. You need a verified email to use favourites.",
  "faqWhatAreFavourites": "What are favourite drivers?",
  "faqWhatAreFavouritesAnswer": "Favourite drivers are drivers you have saved. You can book rides directly to your trusted drivers for a more personal experience.",
  "faqBlockDriver": "Can I block a driver?",
  "faqBlockDriverAnswer": "During an active ride chat, open the menu (⋮) and use Block driver. You can also report a driver after a ride from the rating flow.",
  "faqPaymentSection": "Payment",
  "faqPaymentMethods": "Which payment methods are available?",
  "faqPaymentMethodsAnswer": "Cash, PIN (debit card in vehicle), and Tikkie (payment request sent after the ride).",
  "faqWhoPaysWho": "Who pays who?",
  "faqWhoPaysWhoAnswer": "You pay the driver directly. HeyCaby takes zero commission — 100% of the fare goes to the driver.",
  "faqWhereSeeCosts": "Where can I see my ride costs?",
  "faqWhereSeeCostsAnswer": "On the ride complete screen and in your rides history under the Rides tab.",
  "faqSafetySection": "Problems and safety",
  "faqDriverNoShow": "What do I do if my driver doesn't come?",
  "faqDriverNoShowAnswer": "The waiting screen has a cancel option. If no driver is found within a few minutes, you can retry or cancel the ride.",
  "faqReportIncident": "How do I report an incident?",
  "faqReportIncidentAnswer": "After a ride, use the report option on the rating screen to submit details about what happened.",
  "faqInsurance": "Is my ride insured?",
  "faqInsuranceAnswer": "All HeyCaby drivers are professional licensed taxi drivers with valid insurance.",
  "faqAccountSection": "Account",
  "faqChangeName": "How do I change my booking name?",
  "faqChangeNameAnswer": "Go to Account and tap the name field to edit it. Your new name will be shown to drivers on future bookings.",
  "faqVerifyEmail": "How do I verify my email?",
  "faqVerifyEmailAnswer": "Favourites need a saved email. Open Account or Favourite drivers, tap Add Email, enter your address, and tap Continue. For App Store review, use the review email and enter the 6-digit code from App Review Information in the verification code field.",
  "faqDeleteAccount": "How do I delete my account?",
  "faqDeleteAccountAnswer": "Go to Account, tap Delete my account, confirm by typing DELETE. This removes your rider identity and related saved data from HeyCaby.",
  "termsTitle": "Terms of Service",
  "termsWhatIsHeyCaby": "What is HeyCaby",
  "termsWhatIsHeyCabyBody": "HeyCaby is a zero-commission platform that connects riders with professional, licensed Dutch taxi drivers. HeyCaby does not employ drivers and does not set fares. The platform facilitates matching only.",
  "termsRiderResponsibilities": "Rider responsibilities",
  "termsRiderResponsibilitiesBody": "Riders must provide accurate booking information including correct pickup location and destination. Respectful conduct toward drivers is required at all times. Riders must be present at the pickup location when the driver arrives.",
  "termsPayment": "Payment",
  "termsPaymentBody": "All payments are made directly from rider to driver. HeyCaby does not process, hold, or take a percentage of any payment. Available methods are cash, PIN (debit card), and Tikkie.",
  "termsCancellation": "Cancellation",
  "termsCancellationBody": "Rides can be cancelled free of charge before a driver accepts the request. Once a driver has accepted, the driver may charge a cancellation fee at their discretion.",
  "termsSuspension": "Account suspension",
  "termsSuspensionBody": "HeyCaby reserves the right to suspend accounts in cases of fraud, abuse, repeated no-shows, or false reports against drivers.",
  "termsDisputes": "Dispute resolution",
  "termsDisputesBody": "Any disputes between riders and drivers should first be reported through the in-app report feature. HeyCaby will review reports and mediate where possible.",
  "termsGoverningLaw": "Governing law",
  "termsGoverningLawBody": "These terms are governed by the laws of the Netherlands. Any legal proceedings shall be brought before the competent courts in the Netherlands.",
  "termsContact": "Contact",
  "termsContactBody": "For questions about these terms, contact support through the Account screen in the app.",
  "privacyTitle": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacyDataCollected": "Data collected",
  "privacyDataCollectedBody": "HeyCaby collects your email address (for identity verification), location data (during active bookings only), and trip history (for receipts and ride history).",
  "privacyLocationData": "Location data",
  "privacyLocationDataBody": "Location data is used only during active booking and ride sessions. Your location is never stored beyond the duration of the trip and is not used for tracking outside of rides.",
  "privacyDataSharing": "Data sharing",
  "privacyDataSharingBody": "When you book a ride, the driver receives only your booking name and pickup location. Your email address, phone number, and other personal data are never shared with drivers.",
  "privacyRetention": "Data retention",
  "privacyRetentionBody": "Trip history is kept for receipt and history purposes. Account data is retained until you request deletion. Recent destinations expire automatically after 120 hours.",
  "privacyGdpr": "Your rights (GDPR)",
  "privacyGdprBody": "Under GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, and delete your personal data. You can delete your rider account in-app from Account → Delete my account. For other requests, contact support through the Account screen.",
  "privacyNoAds": "No advertising",
  "privacyNoAdsBody": "HeyCaby does not display advertising and does not sell your data to third parties. Your data is used exclusively for providing the ride-matching service.",
